instruction: Generate a 3-paneled cartoon strip funny depiction of the pandemic.
output:
Panel 1: Two people are standing in a line outside a store, waiting to get in. 
Person 1: I can't believe this pandemic has already been going on for a year! 
Person 2: Yeah, I know. 

Panel 2: Person 1 is looking back at the end of the line, which stretches far off into the distance.
Person 1: How long do you think the line is now? 
Person 2: I don't know.....a mile?!

Panel 3: Person 1 turns back around and they both start to laugh. 
Person 1: And they said "social distancing" was going to be a breeze! 
Person 2: Yeah, right!
